snippet.title: Flutter 3.0 - What's New and Amazing Features
snippet.description:
Flutter 3.0 is here with amazing new features! In this video, we explore all the exciting updates and improvements in the latest version of Flutter.

In this comprehensive tutorial, we'll cover:
- New Material 3 widgets and theming
- Performance improvements
- Desktop and web enhancements
- New platform support
- Breaking changes and migration guide

Timestamps:
00:00 Introduction
01:30 Material 3 Design
05:45 Performance Improvements
10:20 Desktop and Web Support
15:10 New Platform Features
20:30 Migration Guide
25:15 Conclusion

Don't forget to like, subscribe, and hit the notification bell to stay updated with our latest Flutter content!

snippet.title: Clean Architecture in Flutter - Complete Guide
snippet.description:
Learn how to implement Clean Architecture in your Flutter applications. This comprehensive guide covers everything from project structure to practical implementation.

In this tutorial, we'll cover:
- What is Clean Architecture and why use it
- Setting up a Flutter project with Clean Architecture
- Domain, Data, and Presentation layers
- Use Cases and Repositories
- Dependency Injection
- Testing Clean Architecture

Timestamps:
00:00 Introduction
02:15 Clean Architecture Principles
07:30 Project Setup
12:45 Domain Layer Implementation
18:20 Data Layer Implementation
25:10 Presentation Layer Implementation
32:40 Dependency Injection
38:15 Testing
45:30 Conclusion

Don't forget to like, subscribe, and hit the notification bell to stay updated with our latest Flutter content!
